title: Ralf Keidel
text:
Ralf Keidel (born 6 Marc 1977) is a German <a href="Association%20football">football</a> coach and former player. He works as assistant manager for <a href="FC%20Ingolstadt%2004%20II">FC Ingolstadt 04 II</a>.
Career.
Keidel made his debut on the German professional league level in the <a href="Bundesliga">Bundesliga</a> for <a href="MSV%20Duisburg">MSV Duisburg</a> on 31 March 2000 when he came on as a substitute in the 88th minute in a game against <a href="SSV%20Ulm%201846">SSV Ulm 1846</a>.
